<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="1" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#add8ff" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">As a prerequisite to establishing a<BR ALIGN='left'/>corporate reorganization, the statutory<BR ALIGN='left'/>terms of section 368(a)(1)(D) require<BR ALIGN='left'/>that the stock or securities of the<BR ALIGN='left'/>transferee be transferred in a<BR ALIGN='left'/>transaction qualifying under either<BR ALIGN='left'/>sections 354, 355 or 356. It is<BR ALIGN='left'/>undisputed that only section 354 is<BR ALIGN='left'/>herein applicable.</TD></TR>
